  "texts": [
    "The Youku NER dataset functions as an openly accessible resource for NER within the entertainment domain.",
    "Derived from titles linked to Youku videos, the entity categories are delineated into three overarching types (figure, program, misc) and nine more specific types (figure, variety show, movie, animation, TV drama, character, number, location, song).",
    "• Dialogue RE (Yu et al, 2020a).",
    "The Dialogue RE dataset stands as the initial manually annotated dataset for relation extraction based on dialogues.",
    "It originates from 1,788 dialogues extracted from the American sitcom \"Friends.\""
  ],
